snippet.title: Cassette Beasts - Official Pier of the Unknown DLC Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Cassette Beasts is a turn-based open-world RPG developed by Bytten Studio. Cassette Beasts is launching a new DLC titled 'Pier of the Unknown' including a new storyline, a new carnival-themed location, 12 new monsters, 5 new character costumes, and more. The 'Pier of the Unknown' DLC for Cassette Beasts launches on October 4 for Xbox Series S|X, Xbox One, Xbox Game Pass, Nintendo Switch, Steam Deck, PC, and PC Game Pass.
